overview: Naya, who had only known Ary for 2 weeks and was immediately proposed to by Ary, wanted to find out what was behind this too hasty and somewhat suspicious proposal. However, Ary's closed attitude and lies to Naya actually make things worse, making Naya desperate to do drastic things to get the truth and peace, even though the relationship is at stake.
title: Misi Kafe Biru
